  "description": {
    "canonical": "Harmony triumphs over hate. Heavy Attacks condense Status Effect damage into a single instance. Heavy Attack kills empower allies with increased Status Duration.\r\n\r\nExperience the true power of Jade's Ensemble when Evensong, Cantare, and Harmony sing together.",
